description:
Treasure Island (1990)

Charlton Heston...........Long John Silver
Christian Bale............Jim Hawkins
Oliver Reed...............Capt. Billy Bones
Christopher Lee...........Blind Pew
Richard Johnson...........Squire Trelawney
Julian Glover.............Dr. Livesey
James Cosmo...............Redruth
Pete Postlethwaite........George Merry


This movie is long out of print, and was only available on VHS and Laserdisc.  This is a transfer from the Laserdisc.  Great care was taken to ensure high quality video and audio.  The video is encoded at 7500kbps and the audio is 48k PCM stereo, which is why the film is split over 2 discs.

The audio is Stereo Surround, which will output to a 5-speaker setup if your DVD player is capable of decoding it.  The rear channels contain much of the music, and the center channel contains the dialogue.

Petition for the official DVD release here: http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/title.jsp?stid=14882

Until the official DVD is released, this will be the best version you will have!


